contentrichtext.text: '''OKC''' is a [[three-letter abbreviation]]. It can stand for: * [[Keratocystic odontogenic tumour|Odontogenic Keratocyst]], a tumor in the jaw now referred to as "keratocystic odontogenic tumor" * [[Oklahoma City]], the capital and largest city of the U.S. state of Oklahoma * [[Oklahoma City Thunder]], the city's NBA team * [[Will Rogers World Airport]], Oklahoma City's commercial airport (IATA abbreviation) * [[OkCupid]], a dating website * ''[[OK Computer]]'', an album by Radiohead * ''[[OK Cowboy]]'', an album by Vitalic {{disambig}}
